\noindent\textbf{帶領提問 Leading Question}\\[0.2em]
\textit{在這40多個比喻中，哪一個你以為熟悉，卻從未真正聽進去？\\
今天，再讀一次，問：耶穌借這比喻在向我說什麼？\\
Which of these parables do you assume you know, but have never truly heard?\\
Read it once more today — and ask: what is Jesus saying to me through it?}

