%% ============================================
%% APPENDIX G: SEVEN SIGNS OF JOHN
%% ============================================
\chapter*{Appendix G: Seven Signs of John 約翰福音七大神蹟}
\addcontentsline{toc}{chapter}{Appendix G: Seven Signs of John 約翰福音七大神蹟}
\markboth{}{}

\noindent\fcolorbox{LiturgicalGold}{ScriptureBg}{%
\begin{minipage}{6.0in}\vspace{0.18cm}
\centering
{\footnotesize\bfseries\color{LiturgicalRed}\cjkfont\upshape\selectfont 讀經之鑰 \;\textperiodcentered\; The Key}\\[0.4em]
{\footnotesize\color{TextGray}\cjkfont\upshape\selectfont
σημεῖον 是\textit{記號}，不是\textit{表演}。\\
每個記號都在問你同一個問題——\textbf{你有沒有看見祂的榮光？}（約1:14）}
\vspace{0.18cm}
\end{minipage}}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\noindent\textit{約翰沒有用「神蹟」(δύναμις/miracle) 一詞，而用「神蹟」(σημεῖον/sign)，
強調這些神蹟是\textbf{指向耶穌身份的記號}。
John never uses the word ``miracle'' (dynamis), but ``sign'' (sēmeion) —
indicators pointing beyond themselves to who Jesus is.}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\noindent\textbf{總綱經文 The Framing Verse} (John 20:30-31):

\begin{center}
\fcolorbox{LiturgicalGold}{ScriptureBg}{%
\begin{minipage}{5.5in}
\centering\vspace{0.15cm}
{\footnotesize\color{TextGray}\cjkfont\upshape\selectfont
「耶穌在門徒面前另外行了許多神蹟，沒有記在這書上。但記這些事，要叫你們信
耶穌是基督，是神的兒子，並且叫你們信了祂，就可以因祂的名得生命。」}\\[0.10em]
{\scriptsize\itshape\color{TextGray}\latinfont\selectfont
``Many other signs Jesus did... but these are written that you may believe...''}\\[0.05em]
{\scriptsize\color{LiturgicalBlue}\latinfont\selectfont \textemdash\ John 20:30-31 \textemdash}
\vspace{0.15cm}
\end{minipage}}
\end{center}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\section*{1. 水變酒 Water into Wine\quad(John 2:1-11)}
\noindent\textbf{地點:} 加利利的迦拿婚宴 \;/\; Wedding at Cana \\
\noindent\textbf{記載:}「這是耶穌所行的頭一件神蹟，是在加利利的迦拿行的，顯出祂的榮耀來」(2:11) \\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義 Sign Meaning:} 舊約律法的水變為新約恩典的酒——\jesus{}「我來不是要廢掉，乃是要成全」。婚宴象徵末世彌賽亞的喜宴；耶穌就是真新郎。\\
\textit{The water of Old Covenant law transformed into the wine of New Covenant grace. Marriage feast prefigures the Messianic banquet; Jesus is the true Bridegroom.}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\section*{2. 醫治大臣之子 Healing the Nobleman's Son\quad(John 4:46-54)}
\noindent\textbf{地點:} 加利利的迦拿（隔空醫治在迦百農之子）/ Cana (healing in Capernaum) \\
\noindent\textbf{記載:}「這是耶穌在加利利行的第二件神蹟」(4:54) \\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義:} 耶穌的話語超越空間——\textit{just one word from Christ heals across distance.}信心不在乎眼見，而在乎話語。「你回去吧，你的兒子活了！」\\
\textit{Christ's word transcends space — He speaks, and it is so. Faith rests not on sight but on the Word.}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\section*{3. 醫治畢士大池畔三十八年的癱子 Healing at Bethesda\quad(John 5:1-15)}
\noindent\textbf{地點:} 耶路撒冷畢士大池 \;/\; Pool of Bethesda \\
\noindent\textbf{安息日爭議:} 引發法利賽人逼迫的神蹟 \;/\; Triggered Sabbath controversy \\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義:} 律法（池水）救不了，唯有耶穌的話——\jesus{}「起來，拿你的褥子走吧」。本章後續是耶穌與神同等的宣告（5:18-30）。\\
\textit{The law (the pool) cannot save; only Christ's living word raises the helpless. Followed by the great Son-of-God discourse.}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\section*{4. 五餅二魚餵飽五千 Feeding the 5000\quad(John 6:1-14)}
\noindent\textbf{唯一四福音都記載的神蹟 The only sign recorded in all 4 Gospels} \\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義:} 接著宣告\jesus{}「我就是生命的糧」(6:35)。耶穌不僅給糧，祂\textit{就是}糧。物質的餵養指向永恆的餵養。\\
\textit{Jesus not only provides bread — He \emph{is} the Bread of Life. Physical feeding points to the eternal feast.}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\section*{5. 海面行走 Walking on Water\quad(John 6:15-21)}
\noindent\textbf{記載:} 暴風中門徒見耶穌行在海面，\jesus{}「是我，不要怕」（希臘原文 Ἐγώ εἰμι — \textbf{我是}）\\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義:} 此處第一次出現約翰福音的「我是」(Ἐγώ εἰμι)——耶和華的名（出3:14）。海與風是創造之物，順服創造者。\\
\textit{First Ἐγώ εἰμι in John — the divine Name (Ex 3:14). Sea and storm obey their Creator.}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\section*{6. 醫治生來瞎眼的 Healing the Man Born Blind\quad(John 9:1-41)}
\noindent\textbf{地點:} 西羅亞池（譯出來就是「奉差遣」）\;/\; Pool of Siloam (``Sent'') \\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義:} 緊接著\jesus{}「我是世界的光」(9:5)。物質之光開瞎子的眼，屬靈之光開靈魂的眼。\textit{瞎子終於認出光，法利賽人卻在光中盲目}——9章結尾的反轉。\\
\textit{Physical sight opened by the Light of the World. The blind man comes to see; the seeing Pharisees become blind.}

\vspace{0.2cm}

\section*{7. 拉撒路復活 Raising Lazarus\quad(John 11:1-44)}
\noindent\textbf{記載:} \jesus{}「復活在我，生命也在我；信我的人雖然死了，也必復活」(11:25) \\
\noindent\textbf{屬靈意義:} 七神蹟的高峰——\textit{the apex sign.} 不僅治病、不僅供應，乃是\textbf{勝過死亡}。為祂自己復活預備（緊接著就是受難週）。約翰福音中神性宣告的頂點。\\
\textit{The apex. Not healing, not feeding — \emph{conquering death itself.} Sets up the Passion: the One who raises will Himself be raised.}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\noindent\fcolorbox{LiturgicalGold}{ScriptureBg}{%
\begin{minipage}{6.0in}
\centering\vspace{0.2cm}
{\footnotesize\color{TextGray}\cjkfont\upshape\selectfont
\textbf{七神蹟的結構 Sign Structure:} 神蹟1（水變酒）與神蹟7（拉撒路復活）皆是「無到有」的創造行動；中間五個神蹟是「殘缺到完整」的醫治。\\
\textit{Signs 1 \& 7 are creative ``out-of-nothing'' acts; the middle five are restorative healings.}}
\vspace{0.2cm}
\end{minipage}}

\vspace{0.3cm}

\noindent\textbf{帶領提問 Leading Question}\\[0.2em]
\textit{你曾為缺乏神蹟而失望嗎？\\
你忘了——神蹟是\textbf{記號}，不是\textbf{目的}。記號指向祂的榮光。\\
今天，從哪一個記號裡，你看見了祂？\\
Have you been disappointed for the lack of miracles?\\
You forgot — a sign points beyond itself. Through which sign do you see Him today?}

\pagebreak

